name: Scuba Diving Fun - Swim with sharks in deep sea 3D
name_original: Scuba Diving Fun - Swim with sharks in deep sea 3D
description:
Scuba Diving Fun is newest adventure 3D game. Enjoy swimming with fishes and sea life underwater. Realistic graphics and sound effects bring you the real scuba diving experience.

Game is composed of 36+ challenging and fun levels. Mines are deployed along your way under the sea. Avoid mines and hurdles and make your way to the end point.

Compare your progress with the players worldwide through global leaderboard.
